Description: The flight into Egypt, a sketch; a man (Joseph) walking to left with stick, seen from behind, holding a donkey on a lead at right; arch-shaped plate; fifth state with heavy reworking with burin, probably not by Rembrandt. c.1627 Etching
Curator's comments: For an impression of the third state and comment see F,5.118.
